data.description: Welcome to this beautiful and unique property with a mother-in-law suite included. This house has been well cared for and a must see! The exceptional property includes new hard wood floors throughout the entire house and newly concrete and a rock scape front yard. The house includes 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms with a spacious 2-car garage and a lot more parking space available. No HOA and very low taxes. Located only 10 minutes from Downtown Denver and 10 minutes from Northfield shopping center. Don’t let this unique opportunity slip away.
